{"tid":2505753,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本街訪｜姜濤能否進軍亞洲？日本女生大讚靚仔　票選最有好感輸畀另一MIRROR成員","createTime":"2021-04-27T00:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T02:18:05.000Z","uid":271829,"like":31,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"906dac6696858819b04e0b8ec189282826143b18","tid":2505753,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T00:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Aat7bifUkxQIbnCQoYbUyOta8uY=/535x300/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IPA2DAYQIZGUDHRDILCZQOGLEA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAat7bifUkxQIbnCQoYbUyOta8uY%3D%2F535x300%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIPA2DAYQIZGUDHRDILCZQOGLEA.png&h=a2952dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東京街頭訪問，大多人認為姜濤像韓星或尊尼事務所的偶像。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rWk5rcHZvkRkKnw0b374gsuoimA=/535x300/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/336XO4F6QNDOBEZ5WSKUK6SU7U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrWk5rcHZvkRkKnw0b374gsuoimA%3D%2F535x300%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F336XO4F6QNDOBEZ5WSKUK6SU7U.png&h=da1778de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMirror成員中，兩位高中生就對Anson Kong（AK）最有好感。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cr-UVjIIvOPyF3AM7aQcoPUGUpg=/535x300/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5AT2HRQXABDVDLI3XGSIBNOGXA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fcr-UVjIIvOPyF3AM7aQcoPUGUpg%3D%2F535x300%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5AT2HRQXABDVDLI3XGSIBNOGXA.png&h=a660629e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這位女士覺得姜濤很可愛，會受媽媽級的人歡迎，認為他在日本也有能力走紅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/V2KmG-7p91haaYXfDcMCWXBNceI=/535x356/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PF5WUWQTTZE5LBGCRFLT2FX3AM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FV2KmG-7p91haaYXfDcMCWXBNceI%3D%2F535x356%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPF5WUWQTTZE5LBGCRFLT2FX3AM.jpg&h=b982d925&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n問到對Mirror 12子哪位最有好感，最多人選的是Jeremy、姜濤、AK。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n近年人氣十足的姜濤，先前在頒獎禮上說到希望香港歌手可以再次成為亞洲第一。那麼，如果他在日本出道，日本女生又有甚麼感覺呢？而他又會不會成為日本女生喜歡的對象呢？我們請來了海外街坊阿瓏幫忙，拿着姜濤最新的MV片段給日本女性看看，訪問一下她們對他有何感覺。<br />\n<br />\n選最有好感Mirror成員 Jeremy力壓姜濤、AK<br />\n今次街訪，大多受訪者都認為姜濤第一眼看上去像韓國藝人，基本上都覺得他很英俊有型。另外的就覺得他也像日本的演藝公司尊尼事務所的旗下藝人，該公司的男藝人包括木村拓哉、山下智久等等。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210427/U4USIQMXWBHDRL65SUUCXLC3ZY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210427%2FU4USIQMXWBHDRL65SUUCXLC3ZY%2F&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B64sqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=875f658c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210427%2FU4USIQMXWBHDRL65SUUCXLC3ZY%2F&h=bb2e38ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210427/U4USIQMXWBHDRL65SUUCXLC3ZY/</a>"},{"pid":"dba334dc4b7e62a76ba7e6c303a48b2f0cfb01db","tid":2505753,"uid":70274,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T00:50:33.000Z","msg":"下面應該補充 <br />\n一眾韓國香港連登三等公民見到無人識香港人好開心 韓國是佢地係韓國人呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />哭撚左"},{"pid":"75862ffeca79f476b780bac6f3e2fa9e438bdd2c","tid":2505753,"uid":37876,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T01:14:19.000Z","msg":"Jeremy個樣都似日本風格 有少少妖妖地又有少少牛郎feel咁"},{"pid":"568e3657bb87edff2875a9b1189255effbb1d58a","tid":2505753,"uid":110832,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedB